f `tests_passed=false` and `detected_misconception=false`: continue iteration with new adversarial variant.","   - If `detected_misconception=true`: stop loop and trigger `workflows/misconception_triage.md`.","","## Output","","- Final destination:","  - `.tmp/bkt_output_<session_id>.json`","  - `.tmp/report_<session_id>.md`","- Intermediate files:","  - `.tmp/sandbox_input_<session_id>.json`","  - `.tmp/sandbox_output_<session_id>.json`","  - `.tmp/event_<session_id>.json`","","## Edge Cases and Recovery","","- Sandbox timeout (`exit_code=124`):","  - Treat as failure and increment attempts; prompt for complexity reduction.","- Unknown `node_id` in BKT:","  - Re-seed concepts and verify session_init payload integrity.","- Export failure:","  - Retry exporter once; if still failing, surface DB path and schema mismatch.","","## Learning Notes","","- Keep sandbox commands deterministic and avoid network dependencies in tests.",""],"tokenizedAddedLines":[1000000,1000001,1000002,1000001,1000003,1000001,1000004,1000001,1000005,1000006,1000007,1000001,1000008,1000001,1000009,1000010,1000011,1000001,1000012,1000001,1000013,1000014,1000015,1000016,1000017,1000018,1000019,1000020,1000021,1000022,1000023,1000024,1000025,1000026,1000027,1000028,1000029,1000001,1000030,1000001,1000031,1000032,1000033,1000034,1000035,1000036,1000037,1000001,1000038,1000001,1000039,1000040,1000041,1000042,1000043,1000044,1000001,1000045,1000001,1000046,1000001]}],"gitInfo":{"gitInfo":{"gitRoot":"/home/khanh/src/0_github/Tardis-1","branch":"main","commitHash":"fcbc4c272962a55f6dbf1e27d263242d5a96971f"}},"kind":"KIND_ADDED"}